            "inline": [
              {
                "kind": "text",
                "text": "NumPy uses the IEEE Standard for Binary Floating-Point for Arithmetic\n(IEEE 754)."
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "inline": [
              {
                "kind": "text",
                "text": "Errors result if the second argument is supplied when the first\nargument is a scalar, or if the first and second arguments have\ndifferent shapes."
              }
            ],
